CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, Philadelphia edition, May 11, 1940, pg. 15 reads: " A.M.E.'s Open General Conference In Detroit...No.9 - Rev. L.H. Hemmingway, secretary-treasurer of Church Extension Society, right, being presented by Bishop Gregg at the Friday Morning session."
TitMainTitle: Bishop Gregg holding microphone, standing next to Rev. L. H. Hemmingway in Ebenezer AME Church for AME General Conference, Detroit
